.TH PRODBOX_test 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-test \- Named test suites
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox test
.SH DESCRIPTION
Supported automated test commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBall\fR
Run the full test suite
.TP
\fBlint\fR
Run lint and build checks
.TP
\fBunit\fR
Run unit tests
.TP
\fBintegration\fR
Run named integration suites
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox test all\fR
Run the full supported test surface.
